PULM Another reason Pulmatrix is difficult to value is because it targets unmet needs This means there are not many comparable drugs on the market This makes it hard to value drug candidates but gives Pulmatrix significant pricing power The flexibility of Pulmatrix due to their iSPERSE technology also makes their valuation confusing They can license drugs from other companies so their pipeline may be much larger in the future
